data.name: Label1.Text
data.value: The program was hidden in the system tray. This means the program is still running, but in the background. To bring the program back, you can: - Click the message that shows up when you hide it to the system tray - Double-click the system tray icon - Right-click the system tray icon and click "Open" If you want to close the program instead of hiding it to the system tray: - Right-click the system tray icon and click "Exit" or - Go to Settings > Functionality and untick "When closing, hide in system tray"
